<template>
  <v-text-field variant="outlined" hide-details type="date"></v-text-field>
</template>
<template>
  <v-text-field variant="outlined" hide-details type="time"></v-text-field>
</template>
<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref } from 'vue';
// common components
import UiParentCard from '@/components/shared/UiParentCard.vue';
import UiChildCard from '@/components/shared/UiChildCard.vue';

/*Components*/
import DatePicker from '@/components/forms/form-elements/datetime/DatePicker.vue';
import TimePicker from '@/components/forms/form-elements/datetime/TimePicker.vue';
// common components
import BaseBreadcrumb from '@/components/shared/BaseBreadcrumb.vue';
// theme breadcrumb
const page = ref({ title: 'Date Time' });
const breadcrumbs = ref([
  {
    text: 'Home',
    disabled: false,
    href: '/',
  },
  {
    text: 'Date time',
    disabled: true,
    href: '#',
  },
]);
</script>

// ===============================|| Ui Checkbox ||=============================== //
<template>
  <BaseBreadcrumb :title="page.title" :breadcrumbs="breadcrumbs"></BaseBreadcrumb>

  <v-row>
    <v-col cols="12">
      <UiParentCard title="Date Time">
        <v-row>
          <!-- Date Picker -->
          <v-col cols="12" lg="6">
            <UiChildCard title="Date Picker">
              <DatePicker />
            </UiChildCard>
          </v-col>
          <!-- Time Picker -->
          <v-col cols="12" lg="6">
            <UiChildCard title="Time Picker">
              <TimePicker />
            </UiChildCard>
          </v-col>
        </v-row>
      </UiParentCard>
    </v-col>
  </v-row>
</template>
